---

<ApplicationLayout
  title="Alfa Laval Centrifuge Parts"
  pageTitle="Alfa Laval Centrifuge Parts | OEM and Aftermarket"
  description="Alfa Laval centrifuge parts are in stock at Dolphin Centrifuge. With 1000s of parts in inventory, contact us for OEM & Aftermarket Alfa Laval parts."
  category="products"
  categoryLabel="Parts & Spares"
  categoryHref="/disc-centrifuge-parts-glossary/"
  heroImage="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts-hero-1400.webp"
  heroImageAlt="Alfa Laval Centrifuge Parts"
  canonicalUrl="https://dolphincentrifuge.com/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
  toc={toc}
  relatedApplications={relatedApplications}
  relatedProducts={relatedProducts}
  hideBottomCTA={true}
  disableTitleSuffix={true}
>

  <div class="bg-navy/5 border-l-4 border-gold p-5 rounded-r-lg mb-6">
    <p class="text-base leading-relaxed m-0">
      Alfa Laval centrifuge parts are replacement components used to repair and maintain Alfa Laval industrial centrifuges, including disc stacks, bearings, seals, gaskets, bowl parts, paring discs, distributors, lock rings, and related separator components. Dolphin Centrifuge stocks OEM and compatible aftermarket Alfa Laval centrifuge parts for disc stack separators and decanter centrifuges, with parts available for routine maintenance and major repairs.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Alfa Laval centrifuge parts are components for the repair and maintenance of industrial centrifuges. Centrifuges manufactured by Alfa Laval require parts for trouble-free operation. Centrifuge operators need parts for scheduled maintenance.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="/alfa-laval-centrifuge/">Alfa Laval centrifuge</a> parts are always in stock at Dolphin Centrifuge. We carry the complete range of Genuine OEM parts and Aftermarket (generic) parts for Alfa Laval centrifuges.
  </p>
  <p>
    Our <strong>100% compatible, aftermarket</strong> centrifuge parts <strong>save</strong> you <strong>50%</strong> over OEM parts.
  </p>
  <p>
    We have an in-house inventory of over 2000+ Alfa Laval separator parts and bowl assemblies. This large stock allows us to ship most centrifuge parts from stock on the same day. Alfa Laval decanter parts, including bearing service kits and decanter gearbox assemblies, are in stock.
  </p>
  <p>
    If your centrifuge is old and needs a major overhaul or repairs, see the <a href="/alfa-laval-centrifuges/">complete Alfa Laval centrifuge systems</a> we can supply using reconditioned centrifuges.
  </p>

  <!-- ============================================== -->
  <!-- Parts Quote Request Form                       -->
  <!-- ============================================== -->
  <section id="parts-quote-request" class="not-prose my-12 bg-light-bg rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 md:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-2 font-heading">Request Parts Quote</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Send us your list of Alfa Laval centrifuge parts. We respond within one business day with availability and pricing.</p>

    <form id="parts-request-form" novalidate>
      <!-- Honeypot -->
      <div class="absolute left-[-9999px] w-px h-px overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
        <label>Leave blank: <input type="text" name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off"></label>
      </div>

      <!-- Customer info -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
        <div>
          <label for="parts-name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Your Name <span class="text-red-600">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="parts-name" name="name" required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="parts-company" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Company <span class="text-red-600">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="parts-company" name="company" required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="parts-email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Email <span class="text-red-600">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" id="parts-email" name="email" required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="parts-phone" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Phone <span class="text-red-600">*</span></label>
          <input type="tel" id="parts-phone" name="phone" required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Parts list -->
      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Parts List</h3>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-navy text-white text-left">
                <th class="px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Part Number <span class="text-gold">*</span></th>
                <th class="px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Description <span class="text-gold">*</span></th>
                <th class="px-3 py-2 font-semibold w-28">Quantity <span class="text-gold">*</span></th>
                <th class="px-3 py-2 w-12"></th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="parts-rows"></tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <button type="button" id="add-row-btn" class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white border-2 border-navy text-navy font-semibold rounded hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition">
          <span class="text-xl leading-none">+</span> Add Part
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Submit -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-4">
        <button type="submit" id="parts-submit-btn" class="px-6 py-3 bg-gold text-navy font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gold-light transition disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed">
          Submit Parts Request
        </button>
        <div id="parts-form-message" class="hidden text-sm font-semibold"></div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    (function() {
      const WORKER_URL = 'https://dolphin-contact-form.dolphin-centrifuge.workers.dev/parts';
      const tbody = document.getElementById('parts-rows');
      const addBtn = document.getElementById('add-row-btn');
      const form = document.getElementById('parts-request-form');
      const submitBtn = document.getElementById('parts-submit-btn');
      const msg = document.getElementById('parts-form-message');
      if (!tbody || !addBtn || !form) return;

      function makeRow() {
        const tr = document.createElement('tr');
        tr.className = 'border-b border-gray-200';
        tr.innerHTML = ''
          + '<td class="px-2 py-2"><input type="text" name="part_number" class="w-full px-2 py-1.5 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-gold font-mono text-sm" autocomplete="off"></td>'
          + '<td class="px-2 py-2"><input type="text" name="description" class="w-full px-2 py-1.5 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-gold" autocomplete="off"></td>'
          + '<td class="px-2 py-2"><input type="number" name="quantity" min="1" step="1" class="w-full px-2 py-1.5 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-gold" autocomplete="off"></td>'
          + '<td class="px-2 py-2 text-center"><button type="button" class="remove-row-btn text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 font-bold text-2xl leading-none w-8 h-8" aria-label="Remove or clear row" title="Remove or clear row">&minus;</button></td>';
        return tr;
      }

      function appendRow(focusFirst) {
        const row = makeRow();
        tbody.appendChild(row);
        if (focusFirst) {
          const firstInput = row.querySelector('input');
          if (firstInput) firstInput.focus();
        }
      }

      function setMessage(text, isError) {
        msg.textContent = text;
        msg.className = 'text-sm font-semibold ' + (isError ? 'text-red-700' : 'text-green-700');
        msg.classList.remove('hidden');
      }

      tbody.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        const btn = e.target.closest('.remove-row-btn');
        if (!btn) return;
        if (tbody.children.length <= 1) {
          btn.closest('tr').querySelectorAll('input').forEach(function(i) { i.value = ''; });
          return;
        }
        btn.closest('tr').remove();
      });

      addBtn.addEventListener('click', function() { appendRow(true); });

      form.addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        msg.classList.add('hidden');

        const customer = {
          name: form.querySelector('#parts-name').value.trim(),
          company: form.querySelector('#parts-company').value.trim(),
          email: form.querySelector('#parts-email').value.trim(),
          phone: form.querySelector('#parts-phone').value.trim(),
        };
        if (!customer.name || !customer.company || !customer.email || !customer.phone) {
          setMessage('Please fill in your name, company, email, and phone.', true);
          return;
        }
        if (!/^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/.test(customer.email)) {
          setMessage('Please enter a valid email address.', true);
          return;
        }

        const parts = [];
        tbody.querySelectorAll('tr').forEach(function(tr) {
          const pn = tr.querySelector('input[name="part_number"]').value.trim();
          const desc = tr.querySelector('input[name="description"]').value.trim();
          const qty = tr.querySelector('input[name="quantity"]').value.trim();
          if (!pn && !desc && !qty) return;
          parts.push({ part_number: pn, description: desc, quantity: qty });
        });
        if (parts.length === 0) {
          setMessage('Please add at least one part (Part Number, Description, Quantity).', true);
          return;
        }
        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {
          var p = parts[i];
          if (!p.part_number || !p.description || !p.quantity || parseInt(p.quantity, 10) < 1) {
            setMessage('Each part row needs Part Number, Description, and a positive Quantity.', true);
            return;
          }
        }

        submitBtn.disabled = true;
        const originalLabel = submitBtn.textContent;
        submitBtn.textContent = 'Sending...';

        const payload = {
          'bot-field': form.querySelector('input[name="bot-field"]').value,
          customer: customer,
          parts: parts,
        };

        try {
          const response = await fetch(WORKER_URL, {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
            body: JSON.stringify(payload),
          });
          var data = {};
          try { data = await response.json(); } catch (e) {}
          if (response.ok && data.success) {
            setMessage('Thanks! Your parts request has been sent. We will respond within one business day.', false);
            form.reset();
            tbody.innerHTML = '';
            appendRow(false);
          } else {
            setMessage(data.error || 'Submission failed. Please call (248) 522-2573.', true);
          }
        } catch (err) {
          setMessage('Network error. Please call (248) 522-2573 or email sales@dolphincentrifuge.com.', true);
        } finally {
          submitBtn.disabled = false;
          submitBtn.textContent = originalLabel;
        }
      });

      appendRow(false);
    })();
  </script>

  <h2 id="aftermarket-parts">Alfa Laval Aftermarket Parts</h2>

  <p>
    <strong>Alfa Laval aftermarket parts are perfectly compatible parts for Alfa Laval centrifuges. High-quality manufacturers produce generic parts for Alfa Laval separators. They save money and time while providing the reliability of genuine parts.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    Call us for Reconditioned Bowl Assemblies &amp; Bowl Parts for popular Alfa Laval models. We can even rebuild certain Bowl Parts worn out by long-term use. Visit our <a href="/disc-centrifuge-parts-glossary/">centrifuge parts glossary</a> to get familiar with the unique terminology of disc centrifuges.
  </p>

  <hr />

  <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gold bg-navy/5 p-4 rounded-r-lg my-6">
    <p class="font-semibold italic">Industrial centrifuges use special high-speed rated Bearings specially made for centrifuges. Do NOT replace centrifuge bearings with aftermarket, 'off-the-shelf,' cheap bearings.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <hr />

  <p>
    These bearings are not suitable for the high operating speeds of industrial centrifuges. Generic bearings can lead to <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-vibration/">centrifuge vibrations</a> and possibly catastrophic failures.
  </p>

  <h2 id="Parts-Gallery">Alfa Laval Centrifuge Parts Photo-Gallery</h2>

  <div class="not-prose grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10 items-stretch">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <figure class="m-0">
        <div class="h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <img
            src="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/centrifuge-disc-stack-250.webp"
            alt="Alfa Laval centrifuge disc stack assembly"
            width="250"
            height="263"
            loading="lazy"
            style="max-width: 250px; width: 100%;"
            class="h-auto max-h-44 object-contain rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100"
            data-no-lightbox
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Bowl Disc Stack</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light flex-1">Complete disc stack sets for Alfa Laval disc stack separators. Available in carbon steel and stainless steel grades.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <figure class="m-0">
        <div class="h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <img
            src="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/disc-centrifuge-top-disc-250.webp"
            alt="Disc centrifuge top disc"
            width="250"
            height="300"
            loading="lazy"
            style="max-width: 250px; width: 100%;"
            class="h-auto max-h-44 object-contain rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100"
            data-no-lightbox
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Top Disc</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light flex-1">Top disc sits atop the disc stack and directs separated phases to their respective outlets.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <figure class="m-0">
        <div class="h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <img
            src="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/disc-centrifuge-sliding-piston-250.webp"
            alt="Disc centrifuge sliding piston"
            width="250"
            height="168"
            loading="lazy"
            style="max-width: 250px; width: 100%;"
            class="h-auto max-h-44 object-contain rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100"
            data-no-lightbox
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Sliding Piston</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light flex-1">Sliding bowl piston and operating slides for the self-cleaning ejection mechanism.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <figure class="m-0">
        <div class="h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <img
            src="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/disc-centrifuge-nylon-seal-ring-250.webp"
            alt="Disc centrifuge nylon seal ring"
            width="250"
            height="164"
            loading="lazy"
            style="max-width: 250px; width: 100%;"
            class="h-auto max-h-44 object-contain rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100"
            data-no-lightbox
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Nylon Seal Ring</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light flex-1">Nylon seal rings for disc stack centrifuge bowl assemblies. Available for all Alfa Laval separator models.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <figure class="m-0">
        <div class="h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <img
            src="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/disc-centrifuge-distributing-ring-250.webp"
            alt="Disc centrifuge distributing ring"
            width="250"
            height="187"
            loading="lazy"
            style="max-width: 250px; width: 100%;"
            class="h-auto max-h-44 object-contain rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100"
            data-no-lightbox
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Distributing Ring</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light flex-1">Distributing ring channels process fluid evenly into the rotating bowl assembly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <figure class="m-0">
        <div class="h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <img
            src="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/disc-centrifuge-control-paring-disc-250.webp"
            alt="Disc centrifuge control paring disc"
            width="250"
            height="150"
            loading="lazy"
            style="max-width: 250px; width: 100%;"
            class="h-auto max-h-44 object-contain rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100"
            data-no-lightbox
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Control Paring Disc</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light flex-1">Control paring disc regulates flow rates between light and heavy phase outlets.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <figure class="m-0">
        <div class="h-44 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <img
            src="/images/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/disc-centrifuge-small-lockring-250.webp"
            alt="Disc centrifuge small lock ring"
